* Server-less Stamp Rally System


** Change server url.

rally_core.js

var serverDomain = "http://shunsuk.net";
var serverPath = "/rally/rally_server.html";


** Add shop domains to the white list.

rally_server.html 

whitelist: [
    'miyazaki-no-macbook-pro.local',
    'shunsuk.net',
],


** Change shop url

rally_server.html 

pages: {
    'sushi1': 'http://shunsuk.net/rally/rally1.html',
    'sushi2': 'http://shunsuk.net/rally/rally2.html',
    'sushi3': 'http://shunsuk.net/rally/rally3.html',
},
